# Business interpretation of the metrics:
# Recall for class 1 (cancelled) = fraction of actual cancellations we caught.
# In hotel revenue management, missing a cancellation is costly (empty room);
# a false alarm is cheap (slightly more cautious overbooking).
# Therefore recall for "cancelled" is the more business-critical metric here.
